Equipment.name: POWER_SUPPLY1
Equipment.description: Power supply used for device Power cycle.

Parameter.name: CouplingMode
Parameter.description: Enable/disable the couple mode of outputs. Possible value : ALL|NONE

Parameter.name: CompensationMode
Parameter.description: Set the compensation mode. Possible value : (Agilent66319) LREMOTE|LLOCAL|HLOCAL|HREMOTE - (Agilent66311) LOW|HIGH|H2

Parameter.name: SenseProtect
Parameter.description: Enable/disable the sense protection. Possible value : ON|OFF

Parameter.name: OverProtectState
Parameter.description: Enable/disable the over protection state. Possible value : ON|OFF

Parameter.name: CurrentSource
Parameter.description: Configure the current source. Possible value : DC|ACDC

Parameter.name: Resistance
Parameter.description: Set the value of the resistance. Set value to 'none' if the resistance is not supported by the Power Supply

Parameter.name: VoltageProtectLevel
Parameter.description: Set the value of the voltage protection level.

Parameter.name: Type
Parameter.description: Output Type used : NONE | ACCHG (AC Charger) | BATT (Battery) | USB
